Practice scoring engine for teams to use in preperation for the Collegiate Cyber Defence Competition (CCDC).
Quick and dirty solution meant for practice labs.
Recommended set up - ubuntu LAMP
sudo apt-get install php-curl php-net-ftp php-imap php-ldap
copy files to web root directory
edit db.php with your local mysql information
run createDB.php then createTable.php to set up the scoring engine database/table
edit config.php for your specific lab environment
ideas from - https://github.com/reedwilkins/Scoring-Engine
jake bernier - dec. 2016
